issue.title: ENH Improving coverage of MinHashEncoder

repository.name: dirty_cat
repository.description: Machine learning on dirty tabular data

issue.body:
Fix #371 and part of #376 

I replaced the data that needed to be downloaded in the tests with generated ones.

Coverage is up to 98%. Only the _more_tags function is not covered (as in #375)..

Had also to take into account empty strings, which was not the case previously. Linked to #378
Moved up the parameters value verifications to the .fit() method, which seems more logical.
